==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crackaloo
<hw>Crack"a*loo`</hw> }</mhw>. <def>A kind of gambling game consisting
in pitching coins to or towards the ceiling of a room so that they shall
fall as near as possible to a certain crack in the floor.</def>
<mark>[Gamblers' Cant, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cracknel</ent>⟦br⟧
